Name: Clutter's Greatest Hits - Collector's Edition
About the game: The most fun & challenging Clutter yet, with over 2000 puzzles to keep you playing for days and days. So many new Clutter variations mixed in with old favorites for a Quest you'll never forget. The Collector's Edition with 25% more puzzles and additional bonus materials. As always, the Clutter levels are highly addicting and replayable. In addition, there are Sliders, Square Jigsaws & Box Quotes with a new Variation. And wait until you see the Plushies & Pinwheels and Totally Remastered Pop-Up Boxes. You've never seen Clutter this fun & challenging. And as always, the options let you play Clutter the way you want. And Favorites are back so you can collect the puzzles you want to play again and again. New Object Sets & Many New Gameplay Modes Over 2000 levels and a very challenging 100 level Main Quest A Hyper Quest and a Bonus Mega-Mix + a Hidden Demo Reel!!! Hundreds of picture puzzles and 200 new Box Quotes puzzles Randomly generated levels mean endless replayability All New Soundtrack with a Cinematic Feel.
